716619f-b.title: Manhattan: Beach Street - Greenwich Street
716619f-b.text:
Beach Street, north side, east from Greenwich to Hudson and across
cleared area (former site of St. Johns Freight Depot) to Varick Streets.
Auust 3, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same in the opposite direction (westward), from Hudson, across
Collister, to Greenwich Streets. The latter is shown with the Ninth
Ave. Elevated Line thereon.
August 2, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
